snippet.title: "He's Not Guilty" Robert Downey Jr. DEFENDS Johnny Depp (IG LIVE)
snippet.description:
"He's Not Guilty" Robert Downey Jr. DEFENDS Johnny Depp (IG LIVE) 
At a time when Johnny Depp could use any form of support from his celebrity counterparts, Robert Downey seems to have come to his defense. It will not be wrong to say that Robert Downey from the movie Iron Man has evolved from a deeply troubled star into one offer most respected actors. For a person like Robert to have backed Johnny Depp means a lot to both Depp and his fans. Robert Downey has often described the perfect fit for his role in Iron man, just like Depp is said to be made for his role in the Pirates of the Caribbean movie. So, what has Robert Downey said in his statements to back Johnny Depp?
